      <title>泰国起草法律以加快290亿美元的运输链接</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/thailand-drafts-law-to-speed-up-29-billion-transport-link</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国宣布了立法草案，以在该国南部建立一个经济特区，这将为连接印度和太平洋的数十亿美元运输项目铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/thailand-drafts-law-to-speed-up-29-billion-transport-link</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 08:47:18 GMT</pubDate>
