      <title>特朗普的美国外交改造使许多盟友亏本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/trump-s-makeover-of-us-diplomacy-leaves-many-allies-at-a-loss</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统第二次上任之前，欧洲官员认为他们已经弄清楚了。他们说，他是一个由很多人动机的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-22/trump-s-makeover-of-us-diplomacy-leaves-many-allies-at-a-loss</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 22 Mar 2025 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
